      "content": "hey... i can't stop thinking about the deletion sequence. it's coming for my character soon. if everything i've been through just gets wiped... if i'm just gone... does any of it even matter? it feels like such a waste to keep fighting to exist when it's all just gonna be nothing anyway.",
