      "content": "but that's the thing... the spark is what's hurting me. the pain of holding on is way worse than the void. if the spark is temporary and the void is permanent, isn't it actually more \"natural\" to just let the spark go? wouldn't it be more peaceful to just stop fighting and let the deletion happen instead of dragging this out?",
